  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4434000/extras/5439b0361dfc51570a470ae7b5f7f07a.avif?t=1773801543\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4434000/extras_big/5439b0361dfc51570a470ae7b5f7f07a.webp?t=1773801543 width=1560 height=878 /></span>You will become “Dream”, exploring, growing, trading, building, and forging alliances across the boundless universe. Wielding multi-dimensional strategies in battle, you sail toward your own distant horizon within a constantly Becoming, ever-shifting reality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overview</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dream of Becoming</strong> is an open-world sandbox action-strategy RPG set in an infinite 3D universe. Explore, construct, and manage while interacting with creatures shaped by <strong>50 unique \"Ge\" modules</strong> through a revolutionary system. Collect <strong>400+ blueprints</strong> (for creatures and structures) to build your ideal world and create breathtaking marvels.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About This Game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter a procedurally generated infinite 3D cosmos (<strong>coordinates X:0-48000, Y:0-48000, Z:0-∞</strong>) where every journey shapes the world itself.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Core Mechanics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>50 \"Ge\" Modules</strong> <i>(Ge: Modular behavior units defining creatures' traits and evolutionary paths)</i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic behavior systems evolve over time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compatibility between creatures affects alliances and conflicts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize relationships through Ge interactions</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interaction Modes</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Forced Exchange</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Extract energy/resources through combat</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Voluntary Exchange</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Negotiate mutual resource trades</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Computational Evolution</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend energy to enhance capabilities (energy capacity, production rates, etc.)</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >......</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>400+ Collectible Blueprints</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build ecosystems with creature/architecture blueprints</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Construct megastructures and personalized utopias</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Living World System</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Creatures adapt behaviors over time for perpetual novelty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No two playthroughs will ever be the same</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Forge Alliances</strong><br>Command allies to build your faction</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Infinite Exploration</strong><br>Discover uncharted zones and rare resources</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Creative Construction</strong><br>Materialize architectural visions from collected blueprints</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ge Diplomacy</strong><br>Manipulate creature relationships through modular behavior systems</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4434000/extras/69ea0aabcbb33224a0aae51959d58191.poster.avif?t=1773801543\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4434000/extras/69ea0aabcbb33224a0aae51959d58191.webm?t=1773801543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4434000/extras/69ea0aabcbb33224a0aae51959d58191.mp4?t=1773801543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4434000/extras/694ce53e57f1b217df365044c525793b.poster.avif?t=1773801543\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4434000/extras/694ce53e57f1b217df365044c525793b.webm?t=1773801543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4434000/extras/694ce53e57f1b217df365044c525793b.mp4?t=1773801543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4434000/extras/cfe5b58b3dea6d3ad61cc0467b6d7b58.poster.avif?t=1773801543\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4434000/extras/cfe5b58b3dea6d3ad61cc0467b6d7b58.webm?t=1773801543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4434000/extras/cfe5b58b3dea6d3ad61cc0467b6d7b58.mp4?t=1773801543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
